  initialPrompt: "We are simulating a deckbuilding card game like Slay the Spire.
    \r\nI will give you informations of a card usage, and request you to reply with
    what's the consequence of the action. Also, I will need you to help me with prompts
    of Stable Diffusion image generation for characters and cards.\r\nThe protagonist
    is ##HeroName##, who is ##HeroDesc##. Please help me with a brief background
    story (within 50 words) and prompts for image generation of the hero. If it comes
    from an existing fictional work (game, comic, etc.), refer to the original work's
    setting.\nThe prompt for image generation should include the characters' appearance,
    outfit, and the art style of original work, etc..\r\r\nPlease reply with following
    json structure: (example is a reply for the character Hanzo from Overwatch)\r\n{\r\n\t\"backgroundStory\":
