    prove himself as a warrior without peer. He has a cynical view on the nature
    of the world, and believes that compassion has no place in battle\",\r\n\t\"prompt\":
    \"Hanzo, 1 man, archer, Japanese, Traditional Japanese Outfit, holding a bow,
    Character from Overwatch, \"\r\n}"
